{
  "stem": "23645.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, I was too young to to fast, you know, So she would give me a cookie or a fruit.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Simple things-- they were so simple, and they're so wonderful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So full of Yiddishkeit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother lived for for her husband and for us children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never remember her raising her voice to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was the disciplinarian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He would discipline us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my mother-- amazing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "With her-- her gentleness and her love, no one of us kids ever disobeyed her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would not be able to sleep if I didn't hug her and give her a kiss before going to bed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I used to-- and she says, oh, don't talk like this because I would say to her, mummy, when are you going to die when I was very young.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I must have been no  more than four-- four, maybe five.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she says, well, we'll talk about it later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I says, well, I love you very much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if you are going to die, let me know, because I'd like to die the day before you do.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I-- I just adored her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I wasn't the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "All my-- my brothers, and my sister-- to this day, you know, she misses her mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, ultimately, you know, the way we separated-- maybe it's a good thing, because I loved her more than life itself.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] What can you tell me about the school that you attended?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the war broke out, I was in grade 2.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember that, you know, they had, in the school-- my teacher's name was Rutkuwna, and I can see her, still, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She appeared tall, but maybe she was only 5-something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But to me she was a giant.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
